Name: Puzzzle
About the game: Hi! This is Puzzzle , a puzzle platformer where you control Rectangle , who aims to escape the cavern! If you're reading this now, this game is in some pretty intensive development, so keep that in mind - this is more or less an early access game. That's enough from me; I may or may not create a Youtube channel to document this process, but that will depend on how I feel later. -Stephen Walton, 'dev'
